  Locus:
    Page: 504
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Worry
---
There are two days of the week upon which and about which I never worry-
two carefree days kept sacredly free from fear and apprehension. One of
these days is yesterday. ... And the other day ... is tomorrow.
